Package: blindrecalc
Type: Package
Title: Blinded Sample Size Recalculation
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Lukas Baumann and Maximilian Pilz
Maintainer: Maximilian Pilz <pilz@imbi.uni-heidelberg.de>
Description: This package computes key characteristics
    and allows the creation of plots for blinded sample
    size recalculation.
    Continuous as well as binary endpoints are supported
    in superiority and non-inferiority trials.
